com.dhemery.core
Class LazyStream<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.dhemery.core.LazyStream<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of object supplied by the stream
public class LazyStream<T>
extends Object

A lazy stream over the objects supplied by an iterable source. The stream iterates over the items in the order they are delivered by the source. The stream iterates over the items as late as possible.
